RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: La Conner, WA operates under a mayor-council government. Marna Hanneman serves as the Mayor. The Town Council consists of six members. Based on the official town website, the identified council members are Mary Wohleb (Position 5), Ivan Carlson, Annie Taylor, Rick Dole, and MaryLee Chamberlain. A sixth council member could not be definitively identified from the provided search results.
